---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="About Bård Ionson — AI artist and creator of Bard's Freaky Faces">
  <div class="about-layout">
    <div class="about-img">
      <img src="/images/digital_self_sm.jpg" alt="Bård Ionson — digital self portrait" />
      <div class="img-overlay">
        <span>DIGITAL SELF · Bård Ionson</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="tag">THE ARTIST</p>
      <h1>BÅRD<br/>IONSON</h1>

      <div class="bio">
        <p>
          Bård Ionson has been creating art since 2012. In 2018, SuperRare accepted him
          to display art on their platform — one of the earliest crypto art galleries.
        </p>
        <p>
          The Freaky Faces were born out of AI experimentation: using a system called
          <strong>SPADE-Face</strong> trained on the CelebA dataset of celebrity faces,
          Bård learned to manipulate the model and push it toward generating ugly,
          unexpected, freaky characters the AI was never designed to make.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each face was crudely sketched by hand, then fed to the GAN which hallucinated
          the rest of the details. The results were then animated using
          <strong>First Order Model</strong> — giving each character movement and voice.
        </p>
        <p>
          Only <strong>50 Freaky Faces</strong> were ever created. The collection lives
          on the Ethereum blockchain.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="links">
        <a href="https://opensea.io/collection/bards-freaky-faces" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-item">
          <span class="link-label">OPENSEA</span>
          <span class="link-arrow">↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://superrare.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-item">
          <span class="link-label">SUPERRARE</span>
          <span class="link-arrow">↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://bardionson.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-item">
          <span class="link-label">STUDIO SITE</span>
          <span class="link-arrow">↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://sageanomaly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="link-item">
          <span class="link-label">SAGE ANOMALY</span>
          <span class="link-arrow">↗</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);
  }

  .about-img {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-img img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    filter: saturate(0.4) contrast(1.15);
  }

  .img-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.8));
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .about-text {
    padding: 5rem 4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .bio {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    border-left: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bio p {
    color: #999;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .bio strong { color: var(--text); }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .link-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .link-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .link-item:hover { background: #0f0f0f; color: var(--green); }
  .link-arrow { color: var(--green); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .link-item:hover .link-arrow { opacity: 1; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-img { height: 50vw; min-height: 250px; }
    .about-text { padding: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
